flowRoot.flowPara: Do not overlay any graphical elements over the logo.
Do not add decorative elements around the logo.
Do not crop the logo, preserve the whitespace around it.
Use the light version of the logo on white backgrounds.
Use the dark version of the logo on dark or coloured backgrounds.
You can place the logo in the about page of an app.
You can also have it in the footer of your webapp.
Do not modify the logo, including changing its typeface.
